review.name: Dizzying
review.reviewBody: A breathtaking, eerie performance. A MUST-HAVE for any JB fan. "Vancouver" is a definite highlight of this show, making you wish more songs from "Sketches For My Sweetheart the Drunk" were performed. Yet a sad reminder of one of the most groundbreaking artists of the 90's with a musical style that rocked the music world unlike no other of his time.
